  "title": "Resident Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><p>- Resident Surveyor oversees all surveying works for thewhole project.</p><p>- Lead a team of surveyor. Plan, coordinate, monitor andensure their works are accurate, throughout the construction process.</p><p>- Coordinate with respective parties to produce computedplan and relevance endorse plan, and ensure survey control points are accordingto authority requirements.</p><p>- Setting up survey points and level on site.</p><p>- coordinate with LTA Surveyor.<br /></p><p><u><strong>Job Requirement</strong></u></p><p>- Diploma in Civil Engineering or Land Surveying orDiploma in Geo-Spatial Information and Technology</p><p>- Member of Singapore Institute of Surveyors and Valuers</p><p>- Min 5 years or relevant experience</p><p>- LTA related experience preferred.</p>",
