    "description": "<p>Ssangyong Engineering & Construction Co., Ltd is a leading international construction company. Established in 1977, Ssangyong enjoys a reputation as the foremost contractor with outstanding skills in both building and civil projects. In the recent years, we have taken on new exciting projects in Singapore and strengthened our position as an outstanding construction company with our high technology and expertise accumulated from building over 12,000 guestrooms in deluxe hotels, over 8,000 beds for hospitals, luxurious villas and advanced intelligent (computer-controlled) buildings. We are now looking to further strengthen our position in Singapore and look forward to welcoming professional and dynamic individuals to join our highly motivated and dedicated team.</p>  ",
